trans-unit.source: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute marks a component's visibility.
trans-unit.target: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute merker en komponent synlighet.

trans-unit.source: If <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute.Yes"></xref> is present, a visual designer can show this component on a designer.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute.Yes"> </xref> finnes, visuelle utformeren kan vise denne komponenten på en designer.

trans-unit.source: The DesignTimeVisibleAttribute is a hint to the Designer.
trans-unit.target: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute er en referanse til Designer.

trans-unit.source: The Designer will ignore this attribute for components that have a UI presence.
trans-unit.target: Designer ignorerer dette attributtet for komponenter som har en UI-kontakttilgjengelighet.

trans-unit.source: It can only be applied to classes.
trans-unit.target: Det kan bare brukes til klasser.

trans-unit.source: The DesignTimeVisibleAttribute is most useful when you have a control that accepts child components.
trans-unit.target: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute er nyttig når du har en kontroll som godtar underordnede komponenter.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName> control's node items should not appear in the component tray because they are drawn by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName> control.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName>kontrollens node-elementer må vises ikke i skuffen komponenten fordi de tegnes med den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName>
